; ============================================================================
; gfx/title.asm — Title Screen Graphics Data
;
; The title scene (sky, buildings, desk, title text, icons) is a pre-converted
; 256x224 image displayed on BG2.  BG1 carries only the small menu font
; for "CREATE NEW" / "OPEN FILE" overlaid on the desk area.
;
; Palette 7 is reserved for BG1 menu text (white on transparent).
; Palettes 0-6 are generated by the image converter for BG2.
; ============================================================================

; ============================================================================
; BG1 Font Tiles — small 8x8 menu font (tiles 41-55) + blank (tile 0)
;
; The large 16x16 title letters (tiles 1-40) are kept to preserve tile
; indices used by menu.asm which references TILE_A..TILE_W constants.
; They are uploaded to VRAM but never referenced in the title BG1 tilemap.
; ============================================================================

